{"word":"H1413 - גָּדַד - gâdad - gaw-dad' - Assemble","slug":"H1413","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּדַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gâdad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gaw-dad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Assemble"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D3;&#x05D3; - ga&#x0302;dad</b> - <i>gaw-dad'</i><p/>A primitive root (compare <a href=\"#/H1461\">H1461</a>); to <i>crowd</i>; also to <i>gash</i> (as if by <i>pressing</i> into): - assemble (selves by troops), gather (selves together, self in troops), cut selves."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1407\">H1407</a>, <a href=\"#/H1408\">H1408</a>, <a href=\"#/H1409\">H1409</a>, <a href=\"#/H1410\">H1410</a>, <a href=\"#/H1412\">H1412</a>, <a href=\"#/H1416\">H1416</a>, <a href=\"#/H1417\">H1417</a>, <a href=\"#/H1418\">H1418</a>, <a href=\"#/H1424\">H1424</a>, <a href=\"#/H1425\">H1425</a>, <a href=\"#/H1426\">H1426</a>, <a href=\"#/H1427\">H1427</a>, <a href=\"#/H4023\">H4023</a>"}]}